<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-licensing-agency> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We’re the Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency (DVLA), maintaining nearly 53 million driver records and more than 47 million vehicle records. Last year (2024 to 2025), we collected £8.4 billion in Vehicle Excise Duty (VED). DVLA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Transport ."@en .
